---
// QuantumGateMatrix.astro — Shows gate operations as matrix transformations
---

<div class="qgm-wrap">
  <h3 class="qgm-title">Gates as Matrix Operations — The Math Behind the Magic</h3>
  <p class="qgm-sub">Every quantum gate is just a matrix multiplication. Don't panic — it's simpler than it looks.</p>

  <div class="qgm-examples">
    <div class="qgm-example" style="--i:0">
      <div class="qgm-gate-name" style="--c:#06b6d4">Hadamard Gate (H)</div>
      <div class="qgm-flow">
        <div class="qgm-matrix">
          <div class="qgm-row"><span>1/√2</span><span>1/√2</span></div>
          <div class="qgm-row"><span>1/√2</span><span>-1/√2</span></div>
        </div>
        <span class="qgm-times">×</span>
        <div class="qgm-vec">
          <span>1</span><span>0</span>
        </div>
        <span class="qgm-eq">=</span>
        <div class="qgm-vec qgm-vec--result">
          <span>1/√2</span><span>1/√2</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="qgm-trans">|0⟩ → equal superposition of |0⟩ and |1⟩</div>
    </div>

    <div class="qgm-example" style="--i:1">
      <div class="qgm-gate-name" style="--c:#4ade80">Pauli-X Gate (NOT)</div>
      <div class="qgm-flow">
        <div class="qgm-matrix">
          <div class="qgm-row"><span>0</span><span>1</span></div>
          <div class="qgm-row"><span>1</span><span>0</span></div>
        </div>
        <span class="qgm-times">×</span>
        <div class="qgm-vec">
          <span>1</span><span>0</span>
        </div>
        <span class="qgm-eq">=</span>
        <div class="qgm-vec qgm-vec--result">
          <span>0</span><span>1</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="qgm-trans">|0⟩ → |1⟩ (simple bit flip)</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="qgm-note">Every quantum computation is a sequence of these matrix multiplications. When you "run a quantum circuit," you're just multiplying matrices — very quickly, on very special hardware.</div>
</div>

<style>
  .qgm-wrap{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0f172a,#1e293b);border-radius:16px;padding:2rem;margin:2rem 0;border:1px solid #334155}
  .qgm-title{color:#f1f5f9;font-size:1.15rem;font-weight:700;margin:0 0 .25rem}
  .qgm-sub{color:#64748b;font-size:.78rem;margin:0 0 1.5rem;font-family:monospace}
  .qgm-examples{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:1rem;margin-bottom:1.5rem}
  .qgm-example{background:rgba(0,0,0,.2);border:1px solid #334155;border-radius:12px;padding:1.25rem;opacity:0;animation:qgmIn .5s ease forwards;animation-delay:calc(var(--i)*.2s)}
  .qgm-gate-name{color:var(--c);font-size:.75rem;font-weight:600;font-family:monospace;margin-bottom:.75rem}
  .qgm-flow{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:.5rem}
  .qgm-matrix{background:rgba(0,0,0,.25);border:1px solid #475569;border-radius:6px;padding:8px 12px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:4px}
  .qgm-row{display:flex;gap:16px;justify-content:center}
  .qgm-row span{color:#f1f5f9;font-size:.7rem;font-family:monospace;min-width:35px;text-align:center}
  .qgm-vec{background:rgba(0,0,0,.25);border:1px solid #475569;border-radius:6px;padding:8px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:4px;align-items:center}
  .qgm-vec span{color:#94a3b8;font-size:.7rem;font-family:monospace}
  .qgm-vec--result{border-color:#4ade8040}
  .qgm-vec--result span{color:#4ade80}
  .qgm-times,.qgm-eq{color:#475569;font-size:1rem;font-family:monospace}
  .qgm-trans{color:#64748b;font-size:.65rem;font-family:monospace;text-align:center}
  .qgm-note{color:#94a3b8;font-size:.7rem;line-height:1.6;padding:10px 14px;background:rgba(0,0,0,.15);border-radius:8px;border:1px solid #334155}
  @keyframes qgmIn{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(8px)}to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}}
</style>
